OL,3,CM&S profits plunge by more than half
OL,4,Cafter cyber-attack
OL,6,FProfits at retail giant Marks and
OL,7,FSpencer's have more than halved,
OL,8,Ffollowing a major cyber attack earlier
OL,9,Fthis year.
OL,11,FThe attack saw online home and fashion
OL,12,Fsales drop by more than 40% when it
OL,13,Fwas forced to halt website orders.
OL,15,FOn Wednesday, M&S reported its
OL,16,Funderlying pre-tax profits plunged
OL,17,F55.4% to #184.1 million in the six
OL,18,Fmonths leading up to September 27.
