OL,6,FOn a reported basis, the profits were
OL,7,Falmost wiped out, plunging to #3.4
OL,8,Fmillion from #391.9 million a year ago.
OL,10,FThe retailer says the hack cost it
OL,11,F#324 million in lost sales, slightly
OL,12,Fmore than its previous estimate of
OL,13,F#300 million earlier in the year. It
OL,14,Fhas, however, been able to recover
OL,15,F#100 million through an insurance
OL,16,Fpayout.
