OL,3,CM&S profits plunge by more than half
OL,4,Cafter cyber-attack
OL,6,FIn terms of the hit to its bottom
OL,7,Fline, the attack is set to impact
OL,8,Fprofits by around #136 million,
OL,9,Fincluding about another #34 million in
OL,10,Fthe final six months of its financial
OL,11,Fyear, M&S said.
OL,13,FThe group said sales in its fashion
OL,14,Farm dropped by 16.4% as the cyber
OL,15,Fattack wrought havoc, with sales
OL,16,Fonline down 42.9% and 3.4% lower
OL,17,Facross its stores.
