OL,3,CM&S profits plunge by more than half
OL,4,Cafter cyber-attack
OL,6,FThe high street stalwart stopped all
OL,7,Fonline sales for around six weeks and
OL,8,Fsuffered empty shelves due to
OL,9,Fdisruption to its logistics systems
OL,10,Fafter hackers targeted the business
OL,11,Faround the Easter weekend.
OL,13,FCustomer personal data ` which could
OL,14,Fhave included names, email addresses,
OL,15,Fpostal addresses and dates of birth `
OL,16,Fwas also taken by hackers.
OL,18,FStuart Machin, chief executive of M&S,
OL,19,Fsaid: "The first half of this year was
OL,20,Fan extraordinary moment in time for
OL,21,FM&S.
