OL,12,Fmonths of its financial year as it
OL,13,Framps up its cost-cutting target to
OL,14,F#600 million.
OL,16,F"The retail sector is facing
OL,17,Fsignificant headwinds... but there is
OL,18,Fmuch within our control and
