OL,3,CM&S profits plunge by more than half
OL,4,Cafter cyber-attack
OL,6,FM&S reported a surge in activity after
OL,7,Fits clothing, home and beauty sales
OL,8,Freturned online but some competitors
OL,9,Fsuch as Next saw market share grow
OL,10,Fduring the period of disruption,
OL,11,Fsuggesting some online shoppers went
OL,12,Felsewhere.
OL,14,FM&S resumed home delivery in June
OL,15,Fafter the hack, but did not restart
OL,16,Fclick and collect orders until August.
OL,18,FIt said online sales have been
OL,19,Fimproving and the group expects
OL,20,Foverall trading to be fully recovered
OL,21,Fby the end of its financial year.
